
Overview of noun regret

The noun regret has 1 sense (first 1 from tagged texts)
                                          
1. (5) sorrow, regret, rue, ruefulness -- (sadness associated with some wrong done or some disappointment; "he drank to drown his sorrows"; "he wrote a note expressing his regret"; "to his rue, the error cost him the game")

